    <h1>Manuskript</h1>
    <p class="font_size-l">
      Manuskript helps you create fast responsive prototypes of websites to test structure, content, layout, and style.
    </p>
    <p>Manuskript is a modular system following atomic design principles. Think bootstrap, but lean, clear, comprehensible. You’re free to use Manuskript as a blueprint for your own websites, just download the source on <a href="https://github.com/opoloo/manuskript">Github</a> or by pressing <code>Ctrl+S</code>.
    </p>
    <h3>Features</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Automated deployment</li>
      <li>Multiple languages (i18n)</li>
      <li>Integrated documentation (MkDocs)</li>
      <li>Automated image optimization</li>
      <li>SASS/SCSS, Coffee and Sprockets support</li>
    </ul>

